950
01:05:22,461 --> 01:05:25,130
<i>Tangisan dari dalam lubang itu.</i>

951
01:05:26,757 --> 01:05:27,966
<i>Seekor bayi.</i>

952
01:05:28,800 --> 01:05:30,218
<i>Kelahiran binatang itu.</i>

953
01:05:31,386 --> 01:05:32,763
Hollis melihat...

954
01:05:34,139 --> 01:05:35,098
